  |                            ^^^^^^^  --------------- function `add_to_waitlist` is not publicly re-exported
  |                            |
  |                            private module
  |
note: the module `hosting` is defined here
 --> src/lib.rs:2:5
  |
2 |     mod hosting {
  |     ^^^^^^^^^^^

error[E0603]: module `hosting` is private
  --> src/lib.rs:12:21
   |
12 |     front_of_house::hosting::add_to_waitlist();
   |                     ^^^^^^^  --------------- function `add_to_waitlist` is not publicly re-exported
